to call for me when I'm
in the middle of my nap.

40
00:04:29,581 --> 00:04:32,248
-Quit complaining, and
just follow orders.

41
00:04:32,281 --> 00:04:33,514
I've got work to do.

42
00:04:43,981 --> 00:04:44,914
-Rukia.

43
00:04:44,948 --> 00:04:46,114
You fool.

44
00:04:46,148 --> 00:04:47,614
How could you have
let yourself get

45
