Never let your
emotions rule you.

47
00:04:51,514 --> 00:04:53,114
And what could you
possibly do now

48
00:04:53,148 --> 00:04:56,648
with that old piece
of garbage sword?

49
00:04:56,681 --> 00:04:58,248
-Are you just going
to stand there?

50
00:05:01,514 --> 00:05:04,748
-Then you won't mind if I go.

51
00:05:04,781 --> 00:05:06,214
-It's starting!

52
00:05:06,248 --> 00:05:09,181
-I guess I'm going in.

53
00:05:09,214 --> 00:05:09,663
Oh!

54
00:05:09,696 --> 00:05:10,648
She got me!

55
00:05:17,781 --> 00:05:19,014
-I'll take care of you.

56
00:05:24,981 --> 00:05:25,740
-Ha!

57
00:05:30,614 --> 00:05:33,148
How could-- Whoa!

58
00:05:36,848 --> 00:05:39,781
-Oh!

59
00:05:39,814 --> 00:05:40,748
Rukia, get up!

60
00:05:40,781 --> 00:05:42,048
Get up and run away!

61
