241
00:17:32,776 --> 00:17:35,010
-Well, normally I'd
be able to, but--

242
00:17:35,043 --> 00:17:36,110
-Rukia.

243
00:17:36,143 --> 00:17:39,010
Is it because your spiritual
pressure is completely--

244
00:17:39,043 --> 00:17:39,976
what is it?

245
00:17:40,010 --> 00:17:40,850
-Shh.

246
00:17:51,543 --> 00:17:53,043
You got left behind here.

247
00:17:57,076 --> 00:17:57,976
-Rukia!

248
00:17:58,010 --> 00:17:58,476
-I know.

249
00:17:58,510 --> 00:18:00,076
The Bount's here.

250
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,076
Take this girl and run.

251
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:01,743
-Huh?

252
00:18:01,776 --> 00:18:04,276
But I can't leave you alone.

253
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:05,810
-Please don't argue.

254
00:18:05,843 --> 00:18:08,443
Just get this child
to a safe place, now.

255
00:18:08,476 --> 00:18:12,910
[clattering] Ririn, over here.

256
00:18:37,776 --> 00:18:39,743
[scream]

257
00:18:50,476 --> 00:18:52,910
[coughing]

258
00:18:58,276 --> 00:18:59,310
-Throw away your sword.

259
00:18:59,343 --> 00:18:59,810
Now.

260
00:19:05,343 --> 00:19:07,743
-Get your hands off her!

261
00:19:07,776 --> 00:19:11,376
-Well, that depends
on what you do.

262
00:19:11,410 --> 00:19:13,910
I have a lot of patience,
but your silly games

263
00:19:13,943 --> 00:19:15,310
have taxed me to the limit.

264
00:19:22,143 --> 00:19:22,910
-Oh, Rukia.

265
00:19:26,910 --> 00:19:27,710
Grr.

266
00:19:27,743 --> 00:19:28,910
-And don't try
anything funny, or I

267
00:19:28,943 --> 00:19:32,110
promise I'll crush this girl's
head before you can move.

268
00:19:48,543 --> 00:19:49,176
-You monster!

